Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my line of fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Continent of Cruzon. A place where oil isn't found in the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People of the land are all born with a certain ability:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to freely control quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They refine quartz with high flexibility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and create ligaments that can expand and contract at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ligaments control the movement of cams, make wheels spin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and push pistons for compressing air and firing bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People of varying strengths hold the power to control quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.84,0:03:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People refer to their ability as magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any lighter ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mr. Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even two year olds can levitate these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't even do it as a five year old,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an un-sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you back a nice souvenir from the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot took off so he wouldn't have to help with the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like there's anything good waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart Arrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Hodr has summoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water... W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd really find you collapsed here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but King Hodr was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't use anything that moves with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's how he figured I'd be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a clever guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't just a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just you're the first one I've met in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize if I offended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Baldr, a general of the Krisna Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-General? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Athens soldier. This is for—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just two shots?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one enormous bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're shooting from outside my range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.96,0:09:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo! Get up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee, I landed it one of my shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landed on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They only brought out three archaic Golems when we're a fair way into their kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't matter if they fought our nation head to head. We're five times as powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they've focused their units\Non their capital and the border wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The capital, Binonten!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Baldr!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for keeping watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're really a general?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the best one in my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, this only costs 3000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, is this your first time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I came here once when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad brought me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too heavy for the low-rank Golem pilots who can't use a pressure gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even for the high-rank pilots,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would say five sacks is their limit\Nbefore they lose control of their ligaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should modify the experimental\Nclaymore to be wielded with two hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't leave some space\Nopen, it'll become difficult to—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart Arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Si-Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come to Hodr's and my wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was... busy with some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more important than your best friends' wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could name lots of things! Like the harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not that you don't like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you for four years and this is how you greet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you, Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Queen Sigyn's smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that guy anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a friend of the King and Queen from back when they were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of those un-sorcerers\Nwho's born once in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he's survived without using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to know is why the King summoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he wants to reminisce on his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Hodr, I've brought Sir Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check out my chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As his wife and a citizen, what do you think about a king who doesn't like his throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you, citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For insulting the king, you'll pay with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent five whole days to get\Nhere after reading your message,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's how you treat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gram, you've gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming, Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, if you're gonna call me here, you should at least tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Troublemaker Quartet of Assam\NMilitary School going to have a reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Troublemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prince who was always looking at the sky\Nto lose some points and avoid the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a mad scientist who locked herself up in the school's lab
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for three days and nights, no\Nsleep, no food, no water, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of Make-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Zess, who we call Mr. Uptight, completes the quartet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called him here, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.62,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One month ago, there was a coup d'etat in Assam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Athens and Orlando both made armed\Ninterventions and it resulted in Athens' victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, Assam isn't neutral anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to the Athens.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the neighboring countries were at war and none of the news ever reached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not simply a neighboring issue anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't disclosed the news to the citizens yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Krisnan Army and the Athens Commonwealth are already fighting at the city border.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense of the Mizoram Stronghold is tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've also received a report that a small platoon has broken through the grand canyon in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the captain of that platoon is Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I know he's from Athens, and he was also a prodigy pilot,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he hated war more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He enlisted to the army
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he wanted to stop his brother\Nwho's the Commander of Athens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mizoram Stronghold is holding out well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a matter of time until they break through that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the valuable info.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be running away into the\Nmountains with my little brother
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before all of Krisna becomes a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brainless coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even fire a normal rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Highness seems to trust him very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a friend from back when we were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he doesn't seem to be just any colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only man who could stop a fight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,between the Commander of Athens'\Nbrother and the prince of a kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a rather odd person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An odd person?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Hodr!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, is your father well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he passed away last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about his funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one would've come anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He raised two un-sorcerers and went into debt putting me through military school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He truly thought my power would awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fool, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say he's an admirable father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He picked a fight with fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... a Golem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We dug this up last month when we were mining for quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We suspect it to be a millennium old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under-Golem, you may call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A millennium old?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance to Binonten?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About 1200.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigyn's been really intrigued by this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ancient who was in the Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much to our surprise, that ancient doesn't have a trace of ever controlling quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.98,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, this Golem doesn't mobilize with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had several high-rank pilots try,\Nbut not a single one could activate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing more than a Golem mechanic's theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the ancients may have been unable to use magic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and used a different method to pilot Golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A different method?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, can you help research this Golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can further analyze this Golem, we\Nmay be able to strengthen our own Golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hodr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to fight a war with Athens?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say this in front of anyone else, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with the idea of surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Athens has proposed a peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can come in terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of surrendering the entire territory to Athens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the divestment of all noble ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're closing the border gate! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those conditions are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also used to say that it's ridiculous to choose a ruler through inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they firing from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The execution of the Krisnan Royal Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigyn wasn't born a royal, but it includes her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of Sigyn and the Prime Minister, I must act as a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're firing from between two and five o'clock, at least 200 away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to have figured out our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo, go back to your Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't write out the last condition.\NThey had their messenger tell me in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hats off to the Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Loquis wants to take us over, not get on friendly terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Zess was always so pissed about!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You act like it doesn't concern you even when your life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you've already given up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we can't fulfill that stupid condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.32,0:22:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that alarm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under attack!{BS'ed, fyi}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, you must evacuate to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.27,0:22:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Rygart's—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:22:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the king for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! We'll come right back to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do I open this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, then it wouldn't respond to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:23:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll change into anti-human bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.48,0:24:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are these hieroglyphs?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.59,0:24:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smaller letters resemble the language we use.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New pilot re...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.19,0:24:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I kidding, I can't read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tregi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.35,0:24:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.96,0:24:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.63,0:24:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.88,0:24:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of Krisna, Hodr!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.89,0:24:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess, I have achieved our goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.56,0:25:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.38,0:25:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the enemy's response?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.87,0:25:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a new model from Krisna?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.06,0:25:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How high did that thing jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.32,0:25:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.86,0:26:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.01,0:26:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that an Athenian Golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.89,0:26:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.04,0:26:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty interesting, but this is goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.18,0:26:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I moved the legs last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.97,0:26:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I forgot to change the bullets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.50,0:26:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.84,0:26:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a step back when I pulled the pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.80,0:26:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.32,0:26:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll push it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.65,0:27:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.29,0:27:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.86,0:28:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.76,0:28:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.05,0:28:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.85,0:28:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what do I do when it wakes up?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.45,0:28:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I change direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.31,0:28:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The upper levers control my upper body...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.75,0:28:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I grab something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.50,0:28:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.58,0:28:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can hold them off for a...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.66,0:28:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.15,0:28:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.19,0:28:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.61,0:28:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... go call for some backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.58,0:29:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.62,0:29:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Hodr.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.62,0:29:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, King Krisna IX.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.91,0:29:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.87,0:29:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apprehend you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.53,0:29:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.66,0:29:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.94,0:29:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart's inside that Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.08,0:29:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.40,0:29:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to buy time?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.86,0:29:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't pilot a Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.52,0:30:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.75,0:30:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dropping out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.38,0:30:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, it's already a miracle that you were promoted two ranks without using magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.51,0:30:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you quit now, you're just proving that the guys who ridiculed you were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.56,0:30:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't have enough money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.62,0:30:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hard on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.60,0:30:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.81,0:30:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I capture you, I can end this foolish war.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.47,0:31:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you aren't the kind of man to joke, but there's no way Rygart would be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.18,0:31:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.96,0:31:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.30,0:31:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.54,0:31:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.30,0:31:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Baldr!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.79,0:31:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't we defending the wall to keep them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Sakura, I just learned that His Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,headed to the mining site on the other side of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.27,0:31:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.34,0:31:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.89,0:31:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.03,0:31:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.41,0:31:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.12,0:32:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.41,0:32:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Baldr!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.68,0:32:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower your body and aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.12,0:32:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that movement?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.62,0:32:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he uses large caliber bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.77,0:32:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angle your shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go through if you take a straight shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, it's great to see you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.91,0:32:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee! Are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.39,0:32:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.44,0:32:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.46,0:32:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. If you can move, then make your way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.16,0:32:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join up with Erekt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.23,0:32:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess, what about King Krisna?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.34,0:32:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.{BS}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.98,0:32:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walls of shields?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.48,0:32:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.66,0:32:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.68,0:32:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they send their units behind us, we won't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.72,0:33:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.97,0:33:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Baldr, the great general of Krisna.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee, go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.69,0:33:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't overwhelm them with this many units?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.15,0:33:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the infamous brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.40,0:33:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.49,0:33:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make needless pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.48,0:33:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The security of His Highness is our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.36,0:33:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.25,0:33:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.35,0:34:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an enormous bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.15,0:34:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking this into Queen Sigyn's research hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.02,0:34:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't, there's no room in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then make some immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.88,0:34:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.33,0:34:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really fight in the Under-Golem?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.16,0:34:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.24,0:34:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.47,0:34:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.65,0:34:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.59,0:34:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I moved that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.48,0:34:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were researching it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.09,0:34:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.88,0:34:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.82,0:34:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something like a small piece of\Nquartz in the front right part of the cockpit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:34:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.74,0:35:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just moved when I touched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.56,0:35:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.44,0:35:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Write me a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.75,0:35:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.84,0:35:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you did and how.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.62,0:35:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as possible, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.59,0:35:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.69,0:35:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked dinner today.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.86,0:35:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's seafood again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.23,0:35:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.30,0:35:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.07,0:35:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.37,0:35:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't eat yesterday when I left it next—
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.07,0:35:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't disturb him, Cleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.11,0:35:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go relieve Argath from his scouting post.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.13,0:35:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.80,0:35:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.85,0:35:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.19,0:36:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who said you could talk back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.12,0:36:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't being continuously active the only thing you're good at?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.68,0:36:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argath and I need to do a check-up on our\NEltemus' for the second strike against Binonten.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.74,0:36:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know how to adjust the\Npressure output for the jumping mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.40,0:36:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Miss Zero Kills Cleo?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.31,0:36:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm pretty useful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.37,0:36:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.41,0:36:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you proud of besides your breasts that're ridiculously large for a 12 year old?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.86,0:36:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bean dish with my grandma's recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.26,0:36:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.79,0:36:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.68,0:36:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can... do laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.27,0:36:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.59,0:36:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long-term Golem activity!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.40,0:36:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pilot a Golem for hours without feeling tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.89,0:36:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's exactly what I'm telling you to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.20,0:36:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.37,0:37:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Cleo really the one and only\Ndaughter of the Saburafu military family?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.54,0:37:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.08,0:37:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.39,0:37:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argath, it's time to switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.59,0:37:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.54,0:37:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.09,0:37:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lee, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.49,0:37:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.32,0:37:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new Golem I saw with Krisna...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.10,0:37:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its movement didn't exactly match its equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.19,0:37:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that odd one?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.40,0:37:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's nothing we need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.55,0:37:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you don't check properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.62,0:37:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.08,0:37:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.16,0:37:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General True's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.49,0:38:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.36,0:38:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you guys gonna work for?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.78,0:38:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything but sleep with the sun down, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.99,0:38:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're polishing non-responsive\Nquartz to use as this Golem's armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.25,0:38:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were disassembling it because it doesn't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.06,0:38:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't disassemble the inner frame from the outside beyond how it currently is.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.06,0:38:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our technology, we'd only be able to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.85,0:38:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.31,0:38:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What technology did the ancients use to build this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.77,0:38:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so unbalanced...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.25,0:39:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike us, the ancients seem to have based their lives around metals
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.94,0:39:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which are well-suited with heat and oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.84,0:39:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.05,0:39:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the inner-frame is constructed of quartz which isn't exactly fit for heat or oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.52,0:39:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exoskeleton was full of air bubbles due to corrosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.72,0:39:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the inner-frame isn't corroded at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.80,0:39:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you assume they refined quartz using\Ninconceivable technology like the inner-frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.47,0:39:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then their technology for refining\Nflexible quartz was rather primitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.90,0:39:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if it was created in a rush to fulfill one last duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.78,0:39:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth to Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.47,0:39:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.69,0:39:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you rewrite your report?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.42,0:39:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.00,0:39:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this isn't a proper report.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.95,0:39:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.99,0:40:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfectly fine report!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.97,0:40:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.60,0:40:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.66,0:40:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll write, so can you explain to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.52,0:40:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put time into that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.42,0:40:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you crawl out of Mining Site 118?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.38,0:40:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get out of the hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.34,0:40:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I jumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.78,0:40:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was at least 20 mailes deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.81,0:40:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't possibly jump that high without a run!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.48,0:40:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the latest, lightest Golem from Athens can only jump 10 mailes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.15,0:40:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.99,0:40:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Hodr or the other soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.47,0:40:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.28,0:40:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.91,0:40:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the impact when you landed?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.80,0:40:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.14,0:40:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me how it felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.68,0:40:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.29,0:40:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.08,0:40:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, if you could back up a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.78,0:40:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use magic, but I'm still a man, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.56,0:41:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.69,0:41:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please redo the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.42,0:41:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.06,0:41:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.35,0:41:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.68,0:41:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cheeks are deep red.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.26,0:41:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the junk Golem that the ancients were using.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.31,0:41:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General True!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.70,0:41:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.27,0:41:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I just returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.82,0:41:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm here, Athens won't be doing as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.03,0:41:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need more hangars than we could possibly have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.84,0:41:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is junk, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.77,0:41:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrap it. It's taking up space.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.76,0:41:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.02,0:41:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but Queen Sigyn is quite attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.51,0:41:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.68,0:41:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's out of my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.27,0:41:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.90,0:41:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.37,0:41:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a useless blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.11,0:42:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A broken blade, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.51,0:42:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hear that? They're talking shit about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.18,0:42:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it to heart though.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.75,0:42:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened to my brother and I too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.04,0:42:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't pilot a Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.53,0:42:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.63,0:42:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already retreated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.74,0:43:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.62,0:43:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.20,0:43:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gram?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.72,0:43:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh...What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.91,0:44:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zess...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.47,0:44:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Krisna has around 200 Golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.34,0:44:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than half of them have been dispersed between all of their cities for defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.89,0:44:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's safe to assume that\Naround 80 Golems are in Binonten.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.71,0:44:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our intention is to destroy at least 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.50,0:44:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can make them realize
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.14,0:44:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we can annihilate a quarter of the capital guards with only five Golems...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.97,0:44:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr, as wise as you are, you'll definitely surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.79,0:45:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.27,0:45:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go over everything once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.29,0:45:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go over?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.89,0:45:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.58,0:45:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.01,0:45:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're engaged in battle at the northern gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.63,0:45:53.52,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.52,0:45:54.48,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.19,0:45:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's not responding at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.65,0:45:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was working yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.24,0:46:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.51,0:46:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.45,0:46:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.79,0:46:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was explaining how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.24,0:46:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, is Zess back?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.05,0:46:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.27,0:46:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.95,0:46:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,West?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.87,0:46:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was the north gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.25,0:46:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.82,0:46:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.21,0:46:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.00,0:46:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr, do you think I can do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.99,0:46:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does move!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.15,0:46:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.38,0:46:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the glove?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.91,0:46:48.11,Default-alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.89,0:46:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk with Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.75,0:46:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you ask the General to give me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.77,0:46:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk with Zess and make him fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.64,0:46:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he doesn't want this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.75,0:47:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.02,0:47:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.96,0:47:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.44,0:47:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.48,0:47:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.20,0:47:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.95,0:47:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get General Baldr!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.02,0:47:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, 30 minutes after Rygart walked away from that Golem, it lost its light.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.65,0:47:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it never responded to any of the pilots who tried beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.18,0:47:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that we, who can use magic, aren't recognized as descendants?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.77,0:51:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words the ancients went out of their way to carve...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.42,0:51:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let us challenge fate."
